1.) Very cutely said, your sarcasm is ok and mine isnt, I understand that, you're the home team. I'm going to ignore only those which I feel cross the line from now on, like an asshole called "earmuffs", the first on my ignore list, ut if you speak out to me in an ignorant manner then I will respond in kind and if you dont like that you can kiss my sweet ass. My motto is: Tit for tat. I say that enough that I would think you knew that by now.
2.) You pretty much hit that one right on the head. I'm sick of atheists coming into CHRISTIAN forums and acting ignorant and trolling, flaming, dissing and generally acting like assholes so I am returning the battle to them on their forum.
3.) I am enjoying doing the Lord's work letting you people add fuel to your funeral pyres. Why should I do anything else? This is also good for my brain. Improves my cognizance. I'm not here to change any minds. That is an impossible task. An atheist will NEVER change his mind. It is like a steel trap, shut.
4.) Did you miss the part where I said a couple dozen times that I am housebound? lol. 5.) Yes, I loved being on Christian forums, but got sick and tired of atheists coming on there acting the same way I am acting here. The big difference is at least I tell the truth about my opinions. An atheist couldnt tell the truth if it benefitted him. He offer his opinons as fact and expects everyone to accept it without question. Bloviation bullshit. Your scientific studies and interpretations of a book you dont believe in but constantly quote to your advantage are just that...opinions. You wont know the truth until the end of your life and it will be too late for you by then. I spend much time with the people I love here at my house. I have constant visitors, the reason I am on during the night mostly. If I am a nuisance to you then I have acheived my goal.
You arent trying to be an asshole, you just cant help it. You're an atheist, it comes with the territory. Tell you what, ask me any questions in a respectfull manner and I will return the favor. Bloviate and I will piss you off. I dont ask you to accept my opinions as fact so dont ask me to accept yours as fact too.
