How to cure internet rage:
Step 1. Walk away from the computer
Step 2. Have a nice cup of tea
Step 3. Read a good book
Step 4. Realize while reading your book that there's billions of people with access to the internet. People are statistically going to disagree with you. You can't always change their mind. Sometimes it's worth tossing out a cookie on a string and seeing if there's a hint of rational human being, other times, it's fine to just ignore it.
